Althorp Park, Northamptonshire Contest consisted of march then selection. and all bands then sat down to a knife and fork tea in the Victoria Hall. Conductors not stated, but all 5 bands were tutored by Randolph Ryan, so it is a possibility he conducted all of them at the contest. March contest -1st Raunds, 2nd Little Bowden.
